title: Etude House Lash Perm 3 step Volumecara
description: 10g Etude House has come out with a breakthrough customizable, 3-step mascara! This affordable, black mascara will allow you to achieve three doll-type looks. Step 1: Defined, clean volume. Step 2: Full, glamorous volume. Step 3: Dramatic, smoky volume. How to Use Twist the mascara to number #1, and then apply from base to tip of lash in zig-zag motion. If more volume is desired turn mascara in sequence and apply after each setting, until desired volume is reached. Benefits: 3-Volumes in One Long-Lasting Waterproof Smudge Proof
